WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 24=

01:52.100 --> 01:53.100
Chiling Secret Technique

01:53.100 --> 01:54.490
has tempered you for so long.

01:54.820 --> 01:56.050
But you remained conscious

01:56.050 --> 01:57.570
and even slipped out to devour spirits.

01:58.460 --> 01:59.410
You've brought me

01:59.410 --> 02:00.410
quite a lot of trouble.

03:01.130 --> 03:02.290
Your turn.

04:34.050 --> 04:35.100
You truly are someone

04:35.100 --> 04:36.170
even He Simu is wary of.

04:37.290 --> 04:38.540
Chiling Secret Technique

04:39.540 --> 04:41.140
can't completely subdue you either.

04:50.610 --> 04:51.850
Young Master Xu is finally back.

04:52.020 --> 04:52.860
That's right.

04:55.170 --> 04:56.980
Young Master Xu is back.

04:57.220 --> 04:58.410
- He's back.
- Young Master.

04:58.410 --> 04:59.660
You're finally back.

05:00.020 --> 05:00.900
(Duan Mansion)
We missed you.

05:00.900 --> 05:01.900
Young Master looks good.

05:01.900 --> 05:03.050
- Young Master.
- Greetings.

05:03.640 --> 05:04.480
Come on.

05:04.490 --> 05:05.370
- Yeah.
- Let's go.

05:05.370 --> 05:06.210
Go get the luggage.

05:12.660 --> 05:15.820
(Duan Mansion)

05:21.810 --> 05:22.650
Feel unfamiliar?

05:24.290 --> 05:25.130
Scared?

05:34.250 --> 05:35.090
So do I.

05:36.980 --> 05:37.820
I feel the same.

05:40.580 --> 05:41.420
Xu!

05:41.860 --> 05:42.700
He brought back

05:42.700 --> 05:43.540
quite a few things.

05:43.730 --> 05:44.570
Xu.

05:44.580 --> 05:45.420
Leave this to me.

05:45.420 --> 05:46.610
You're finally back.

05:46.610 --> 05:48.220
I missed you so much.

05:51.250 --> 05:52.460
Let me see if you've grown.

05:52.810 --> 05:53.660
I've grown taller.

05:53.850 --> 05:54.700
Much taller.

05:56.700 --> 05:57.540
How nice.

05:58.740 --> 05:59.580
Let's go.

05:59.580 --> 06:00.420
Don't stand here.

06:00.580 --> 06:01.420
We'll go in and talk.

06:01.900 --> 06:02.740
All right.

06:03.900 --> 06:04.810
Hey, you.

06:04.810 --> 06:06.220
Move his things in.

06:06.410 --> 06:07.250
Be very careful.

06:07.540 --> 06:08.460
Move them gently.

06:09.490 --> 06:10.330
Xu.

06:10.850 --> 06:12.100
When I was away,

06:12.100 --> 06:13.140
did you cause any trouble?

06:14.170 --> 06:15.010
Are you kidding?

06:15.140 --> 06:16.700
Without me, this mansion wouldn't be

06:16.900 --> 06:17.740
in perfect order.

06:17.740 --> 06:22.900
(Duan Mansion)

06:22.900 --> 06:23.740
Oh, Xu.

06:24.100 --> 06:25.410
I take care of everything

06:25.580 --> 06:26.420
from family expenses

06:26.660 --> 06:28.540
to the arrangement of servants.

06:39.490 --> 06:40.490
This is my sworn brother,

06:41.050 --> 06:41.890
Xue Chenying.

06:42.540 --> 06:43.610
He'll be living here.

06:44.900 --> 06:45.740
Chenying,

06:46.020 --> 06:47.220
this is my sister Duan Jingyuan.

06:48.050 --> 06:49.020
Call her Jingyuan.

06:49.660 --> 06:50.500
Greetings, Jingyuan.

06:56.020 --> 06:56.900
Xu.

06:57.810 --> 06:59.050
Your sworn brother

06:59.370 --> 07:00.540
looks a little bit rustic.

07:03.850 --> 07:04.690
Leave him to me.

07:05.140 --> 07:06.100
Within one year,

07:06.370 --> 07:07.610
I'll make him

07:08.140 --> 07:09.540
a young gentleman in Nandu.

07:10.540 --> 07:11.380
No need.

07:11.810 --> 07:12.850
He'll go with me

07:12.850 --> 07:13.690
to the battlefield.

07:14.070 --> 07:14.920
Don't turn him

07:14.930 --> 07:16.080
into some dandy in Nandu.

07:16.460 --> 07:17.900
I won't.

07:18.580 --> 07:19.780
Go back to the army?

07:33.660 --> 07:34.500
Father.

07:35.700 --> 07:36.540
Haven't you had

07:37.020 --> 07:38.220
enough injuries already?

09:38.370 --> 09:39.210
Jiang Ai,

09:39.820 --> 09:40.850
are you going to rebel?

09:42.460 --> 09:43.300
You and I

09:43.300 --> 09:44.730
serve our own ambitions.

09:44.940 --> 09:45.780
Let's not

09:45.940 --> 09:47.060
accuse each other.

09:47.580 --> 09:49.700
You colluded with a traitor
and plotted treachery.

09:50.300 --> 09:51.250
By law, you deserve

09:51.250 --> 09:52.250
the death penalty.

09:52.530 --> 09:53.820
You've always been picking on me.

09:54.340 --> 09:55.340
You think you will rule

09:55.530 --> 09:56.730
after I'm eliminated?

10:04.890 --> 10:05.850
Greetings, Your Grace.

10:07.460 --> 10:08.340
Why are you fighting?

10:09.300 --> 10:10.140
Your Grace,

10:10.370 --> 10:11.490
when I led my men

10:11.490 --> 10:12.610
to hunt down Bai Sanxing,

10:13.100 --> 10:14.250
I suddenly spotted him.

10:14.940 --> 10:15.780
I tracked him here,

10:16.060 --> 10:16.900
only to see Jiang Ai

10:16.910 --> 10:18.100
meeting with him

10:18.850 --> 10:20.100
very closely.

10:20.300 --> 10:21.180
I tried to arrest him,

10:21.850 --> 10:22.690
but Jiang Ai

10:23.100 --> 10:24.940
helped him escape.

10:25.180 --> 10:26.020
I told you.

10:26.250 --> 10:27.490
That wasn't Bai Sanxing.

10:27.730 --> 10:28.980
Then why did you let him go?

10:30.010 --> 10:30.850
Your Grace,

10:30.850 --> 10:31.700
I also tracked him

10:31.710 --> 10:32.890
all the way here.

11:05.650 --> 11:06.730
If Yan Ke hadn't interfered,

11:07.010 --> 11:08.300
I would have caught him.

11:09.010 --> 11:11.220
Maybe you deliberately attacked me

11:11.220 --> 11:12.250
just to let him go.

11:12.250 --> 11:13.180
Your Grace,

11:13.180 --> 11:14.340
Jiang Ai acted suspiciously.

11:14.650 --> 11:16.010
She must be involved

11:16.250 --> 11:17.700
in Bai Sanxing's escape.

11:22.940 --> 11:24.530
Jiang Ai failed to arrest the suspect.

11:25.010 --> 11:26.130
She'll be punished.

11:26.460 --> 11:27.610
- No way.
- Yes.

11:31.420 --> 11:32.500
- Stop!
- Yan.

11:35.250 --> 11:36.090
Your Grace,

11:36.610 --> 11:37.980
you can't favor Jiang Ai like that.

11:38.580 --> 11:39.730
She's obviously disloyal.

11:40.980 --> 11:42.850
All spirits in the Void are disloyal.

11:43.100 --> 11:43.940
But I'm not.

11:45.770 --> 11:47.010
If you weren't,

11:47.890 --> 11:49.340
you wouldn't have stayed.

11:53.980 --> 11:55.100
I won't deny

11:55.490 --> 11:56.580
that I chose your side

11:56.850 --> 11:57.690
to seek a wise master

11:58.060 --> 11:59.370
and greater power.

12:00.300 --> 12:01.850
But it's been 300 years.

12:02.460 --> 12:03.730
We suppressed the rebellion

12:03.730 --> 12:04.770
and enacted the decrees.

12:05.700 --> 12:07.010
Through all these things,

12:07.770 --> 12:08.820
you've also become

12:08.820 --> 12:09.700
my obsession.

12:10.980 --> 12:11.820
So?

12:19.130 --> 12:19.970
I'm the only one

12:20.890 --> 12:22.490
who truly cares about you.

12:23.300 --> 12:24.820
I can give you anything you want

12:24.820 --> 12:26.300
and solve all your problems.

12:27.770 --> 12:28.610
Simu,

12:29.940 --> 12:31.370
you should trust me.

12:35.100 --> 12:36.490
It was just a casual comment.

12:37.100 --> 12:38.370
Why are you being so serious?

12:40.130 --> 12:41.460
I certainly trust you.

12:43.060 --> 12:44.180
But do you trust me?

12:47.460 --> 12:48.530
I came here upon receiving

12:48.530 --> 12:49.420
Jiang Ai's message.

12:50.060 --> 12:51.060
Now, we're in need

12:51.060 --> 12:51.900
of capable hands.

12:52.890 --> 12:54.730
If you and Jiang Ai suspect each other,

12:54.980 --> 12:56.490
other lords will grow suspicious too.

12:58.980 --> 12:59.820
Yan.

13:05.460 --> 13:06.370
I don't want

13:06.370 --> 13:07.250
another tragedy.

13:16.650 --> 13:17.490
Sorry, Simu.

13:18.340 --> 13:19.610
I was too thoughtless.

13:25.180 --> 13:26.020
As the Right Hand,

13:27.300 --> 13:28.850
you do everything for the Void's safety.

13:35.130 --> 13:36.300
And you're also my friend.

13:38.010 --> 13:38.980
Beside my throne,

13:40.490 --> 13:42.010
there will always be a place for you.

13:46.610 --> 13:47.450
Don't worry.

13:48.490 --> 13:49.420
I promise

13:49.420 --> 13:50.650
to clear all obstacles for you.

14:02.980 --> 14:04.220
Father, you're coughing again.

14:08.940 --> 14:09.940
I'm simply

14:10.130 --> 14:10.970
in poor health.

14:11.180 --> 14:12.020
It's just a relapse.

14:12.770 --> 14:13.610
Take a seat.

14:15.220 --> 14:16.060
I'm almost recovered

14:16.060 --> 14:16.900
from my injuries.

14:17.940 --> 14:18.820
I can stand.

14:20.700 --> 14:22.770
What plans do you have for the future?

14:24.420 --> 14:25.460
The battlefield is cruel.

14:26.340 --> 14:27.220
When you were there,

14:27.420 --> 14:28.370
you were badly wounded.

14:28.890 --> 14:29.730
Don't go back there.

14:30.980 --> 14:32.130
Now you only have a sinecure.

14:32.700 --> 14:34.580
But Chancellor Du and I support you.

14:36.250 --> 14:37.980
Your experience in the army may get you

14:37.980 --> 14:39.460
into the Bureau of Military Affairs

14:39.770 --> 14:40.610
to work accordingly.

14:41.650 --> 14:43.770
Your two brothers
died on the battlefield.

14:44.770 --> 14:46.420
You must not follow in their footsteps.

14:49.490 --> 14:50.330
Yes.

14:51.770 --> 14:52.610
I'll do as you say.

14:59.940 --> 15:00.780
Shunxi,

15:01.300 --> 15:02.580
when you're back here,

15:04.420 --> 15:06.490
you should get married and have children

15:07.420 --> 15:08.730
to carry on our family line.

15:12.980 --> 15:14.010
I'm not familiar

15:14.250 --> 15:15.090
with ladies in Nandu.

15:16.220 --> 15:17.060
Father,

15:18.010 --> 15:19.100
who do you recommend?

15:21.060 --> 15:22.820
Go get those three scroll paintings.

15:25.340 --> 15:27.250
Suyi, the third child
of Vice Minister Wang.

15:27.650 --> 15:29.820
Changling, the fifth child
of Academician Lu.

15:30.610 --> 15:32.370
Qiuyan, the fourth child of Prince Xie.

15:32.890 --> 15:34.730
Their portraits and birth details.

15:35.420 --> 15:36.260
Take a look

15:36.580 --> 15:37.650
and see if you like anyone.

15:46.250 --> 15:47.090
I heard

15:47.700 --> 15:49.130
there was a lady

15:49.850 --> 15:50.890
who grew up with you

15:51.940 --> 15:52.980
as your childhood friend.

15:54.820 --> 15:55.700
After you married

15:55.700 --> 15:56.540
my mother,

15:57.250 --> 15:58.090
she left.

16:01.850 --> 16:02.690
I also heard

16:03.770 --> 16:04.650
Mother was betrothed

16:04.650 --> 16:05.700
to someone else.

16:05.860 --> 16:06.700
But that man

16:06.700 --> 16:07.980
was implicated in a treason case

16:07.980 --> 16:08.820
and was executed.

16:09.820 --> 16:11.060
You reinvestigated that case

16:12.340 --> 16:13.370
and vindicated him.

16:16.850 --> 16:18.220
Now you want me to get married.

16:18.730 --> 16:19.650
So I'd like to ask you.

16:20.530 --> 16:21.490
Do you still remember

16:23.650 --> 16:25.010
what that lady looked like?

16:28.700 --> 16:29.770
And have you ever regretted

16:31.300 --> 16:32.370
marrying my mother?

16:41.060 --> 16:42.460
You have feelings for someone?

16:51.300 --> 16:52.140
After your marriage,

16:52.850 --> 16:53.890
you may take her

16:54.370 --> 16:55.210
as your concubine.

17:01.060 --> 17:02.770
Then the lady you loved...

17:04.220 --> 17:05.180
Why didn't she end up

17:05.180 --> 17:06.020
as your concubine?

17:21.050 --> 17:22.290
If that's all,

17:23.420 --> 17:24.260
I'll take my leave.

17:27.140 --> 17:27.980
Wait.

17:29.380 --> 17:30.460
When you're back here,

17:31.090 --> 17:32.490
all eyes are on you.

17:33.220 --> 17:34.140
Remember.

17:34.140 --> 17:35.140
Be discreet.

17:36.050 --> 17:37.700
Especially in dealing with Fang Xianye.

17:38.400 --> 17:39.250
He is now

17:39.270 --> 17:40.860
the literary leader of Nandu.

17:41.290 --> 17:42.180
Those haughty censors

17:42.180 --> 17:43.420
in the Censorate

17:43.660 --> 17:45.380
deeply admire his essays and poems.

17:46.660 --> 17:47.500
You must not

17:48.380 --> 17:49.490
confront him head-on.

17:52.700 --> 17:53.540
Yes.

18:04.700 --> 18:06.010
Eavesdropping again?

18:07.570 --> 18:08.410
Xu,

18:09.140 --> 18:10.250
is Fang Xianye

18:10.700 --> 18:11.570
the one

18:11.570 --> 18:12.420
who impeached you

18:12.620 --> 18:13.940
and got you exiled to the border?

18:15.980 --> 18:18.160
Why is he always against you?

18:18.490 --> 18:19.860
Does he have a grudge against us?

18:21.180 --> 18:22.020
Yes.

18:22.570 --> 18:23.730
What's so strange about that?

18:24.140 --> 18:25.380
Now, everyone has a grudge

18:25.380 --> 18:26.220
against someone else.

18:27.290 --> 18:28.250
You and I had one too.

18:29.010 --> 18:30.490
What was that?

18:31.050 --> 18:32.620
In childhood, you stole osmanthus cakes

18:32.620 --> 18:33.490
and framed me.

18:33.900 --> 18:34.740
And you used to claim

18:35.090 --> 18:36.660
that I treated you better in Daizhou.

18:38.050 --> 18:39.660
That was ages ago.

18:39.660 --> 18:40.570
Don't be so vindictive.

18:40.570 --> 18:41.410
Glad you know that.

18:42.380 --> 18:43.250
When you were eight,

18:43.250 --> 18:44.380
you stayed there for three months.

18:45.380 --> 18:46.460
But you still talk about it.

18:47.700 --> 18:48.540
Well, who would know?

18:49.090 --> 18:50.220
Who would know

18:50.220 --> 18:51.980
that gentle boy in childhood

18:52.380 --> 18:54.290
could grow up to have

18:54.290 --> 18:55.530
such a sharp tongue?

18:55.980 --> 18:56.860
I'll keep saying that.

18:56.860 --> 18:58.010
A hundred times more.

18:58.730 --> 18:59.570
Xu,

18:59.770 --> 19:01.010
you turned out different.

19:16.460 --> 19:17.300
Xu,

19:19.700 --> 19:21.050
will you really get married?

19:32.220 --> 19:33.060
Perhaps.

20:20.140 --> 20:21.620
There seem to be

20:22.620 --> 20:23.810
quite a few puppet soldiers.

20:35.460 --> 20:36.300
Did you summon me

20:36.810 --> 20:38.050
for the puppet problem?

20:48.490 --> 20:49.810
I released the puppets

20:50.460 --> 20:51.940
to mess up the Void

20:51.940 --> 20:52.980
in the name of Bai Sanxing.

20:53.620 --> 20:54.460
We can strike

20:54.770 --> 20:55.980
when the time is right.

21:01.290 --> 21:03.330
"You've worked hard these days.

21:08.180 --> 21:09.090
You did a great job.

21:09.810 --> 21:11.010
You helped me a great deal."

21:17.820 --> 21:18.660
Did you expect

21:18.660 --> 21:19.770
I would say that?

21:22.490 --> 21:23.330
Yan Ke,

21:23.810 --> 21:25.140
what did I do wrong?

21:26.570 --> 21:27.940
Where's Bai Sanxing?

21:28.250 --> 21:29.090
I don't know.

21:29.530 --> 21:30.860
I really don't know.

21:31.050 --> 21:31.890
I...

21:39.220 --> 21:40.340
(Yan Zhang)

21:41.330 --> 21:42.420
You went to Qifeng House.

21:43.250 --> 21:44.700
You cast a spell

21:44.700 --> 21:45.980
on this ledger.

21:49.570 --> 21:50.410
That's so you.

21:51.570 --> 21:52.860
My little tricks

21:52.860 --> 21:53.940
can never escape you.

21:54.490 --> 21:55.420
After Bai Sanxing left

21:55.420 --> 21:56.570
the Nine-Square Maze Prison,

21:56.570 --> 21:58.490
you sent batches of spirits
to Qifeng House

21:58.490 --> 21:59.730
for him to drain their power.

21:59.940 --> 22:00.780
That's right.

22:16.980 --> 22:18.420
Where's Bai Sanxing?

22:24.490 --> 22:26.700
You've regarded him as a mortal threat.

22:28.010 --> 22:29.700
I just tried to help you eliminate him.

22:37.900 --> 22:39.730
Say your name.

22:53.980 --> 22:55.050
That day, I used a spell

22:55.250 --> 22:56.770
to blur Xusheng's memory

22:56.770 --> 22:58.010
and entered the Prison.

22:58.620 --> 22:59.570
I found Bai Sanxing.

23:13.140 --> 23:14.090
He had strong power.

23:15.090 --> 23:16.700
I couldn't fully manipulate him.

23:45.140 --> 23:46.660
I turned him into a puppet

23:46.900 --> 23:47.740
and brought him out.

23:49.090 --> 23:49.930
Surprised?

23:50.860 --> 23:52.860
I managed to take him out of the Prison.

23:53.530 --> 23:54.460
You once suspected

23:54.460 --> 23:56.220
that his soul candle was still burning.

23:56.380 --> 23:57.380
I guess it's true.

24:03.050 --> 24:04.940
I ordered you to kill Bai Sanxing.

24:05.660 --> 24:06.810
But you acted on your own

24:06.810 --> 24:07.810
and released him.

24:10.220 --> 24:11.770
How dare you defy me?

24:13.180 --> 24:14.860
I did all that for you.

24:16.220 --> 24:17.420
You're the Right Hand,

24:17.810 --> 24:19.530
second only to the Sovereign!

24:20.290 --> 24:21.810
You have the strongest desire

24:21.810 --> 24:22.770
for the throne!

24:23.050 --> 24:24.180
How can you stand

24:24.180 --> 24:25.140
being beneath He Simu?

24:28.940 --> 24:30.460
When Bai Sanxing is creating chaos,

24:31.330 --> 24:32.940
you can eliminate He Simu

24:33.380 --> 24:34.570
and become the Sovereign.

24:35.220 --> 24:36.700
If you dare to hurt Simu,

24:37.250 --> 24:39.090
I'll kill you now!

24:50.420 --> 24:51.260
All right.

24:51.700 --> 24:52.810
You can kill me.

24:53.660 --> 24:54.700
If I die,

24:55.090 --> 24:56.530
He Simu will die too!

25:01.670 --> 25:02.530
She's the one

25:02.530 --> 25:03.460
Bai Sanxing hates most.

25:04.810 --> 25:05.770
Now, he has regained

25:05.770 --> 25:06.620
his power.

25:09.460 --> 25:10.860
Only I can control him.

25:12.770 --> 25:14.010
If I'm dead,

25:14.530 --> 25:15.570
he'll lose control.

25:16.250 --> 25:17.380
Then he'll hunt He Simu

25:17.380 --> 25:18.700
without giving up.

25:20.010 --> 25:20.850
However,

25:22.140 --> 25:23.860
I may show some mercy

25:25.180 --> 25:26.180
and keep her alive.

25:43.980 --> 25:44.820
No spirit

25:45.530 --> 25:46.660
can compare to you.

25:49.980 --> 25:51.490
After I use Chiling Secret Technique

25:52.330 --> 25:53.460
to drain all the power

25:53.460 --> 25:54.810
of He Simu...

25:56.010 --> 25:56.850
Yan Ke,

25:58.940 --> 26:00.010
I will make you

26:00.010 --> 26:01.380
the supreme sovereign.

26:02.250 --> 26:03.090
And I...

26:06.490 --> 26:07.980
I'll be your consort.

26:16.050 --> 26:16.890
You...

26:17.660 --> 26:19.700
Want to be my consort?

26:20.730 --> 26:21.570
Yes.

26:22.010 --> 26:22.850
I promise you.

26:23.420 --> 26:24.620
I'll spare her life then.

26:34.940 --> 26:35.780
All right.

26:37.290 --> 26:38.420
What are you going to do?

26:39.250 --> 26:40.140
Just trust me.

26:41.050 --> 26:42.050
I'll handle everything.

26:45.180 --> 26:46.020
Deal.

26:56.250 --> 26:57.090
(Simu,)

26:58.010 --> 26:59.010
(I'm back here in Nandu.)

27:00.420 --> 27:01.700
(The court seems stable,)

27:02.140 --> 27:03.380
(but undercurrents are surging.)

27:04.700 --> 27:06.570
(Before recovering
the 17 Prefectures in north)

27:07.220 --> 27:09.010
(the unrest will not end.)

27:10.010 --> 27:11.530
(Soon, I'll go back to the army.)

27:51.090 --> 27:51.930
Hey, everybody.

27:52.140 --> 27:53.140
Last night, Bai Sanxing

27:53.460 --> 27:54.490
devoured my two vice lords

27:54.700 --> 27:55.770
and three senior officials.

27:56.380 --> 27:57.330
If this continues,

27:57.330 --> 27:58.530
even I will be devoured

27:58.530 --> 27:59.370
by him.

28:05.180 --> 28:06.020
Stop pacing.

28:06.490 --> 28:07.980
- You make me dizzy.
- But...

28:07.980 --> 28:09.250
You're not alone in suffering.

28:09.660 --> 28:10.500
When Her Grace comes,

28:10.770 --> 28:11.770
we'll find a solution.

28:11.770 --> 28:13.770
He's devoured so many powerful spirits.

28:13.770 --> 28:15.220
His own power must have skyrocketed.

28:15.220 --> 28:16.730
This will lead to big trouble.

28:17.380 --> 28:18.780
- Yeah.
- That's right.

28:25.860 --> 28:27.090
Why hasn't Her Grace come yet?

28:33.330 --> 28:34.730
Her Grace ordered us

28:35.050 --> 28:36.880
to call off the assembly for three days.

28:37.220 --> 28:38.250
So everybody,

28:38.250 --> 28:39.140
you may leave.

28:40.180 --> 28:41.050
Our world is in chaos.

28:41.180 --> 28:42.770
We need Her Grace to lead us.

28:42.770 --> 28:44.180
Why did she call off the assembly?

28:44.490 --> 28:45.810
What... What shall we do?

28:47.180 --> 28:48.940
Her Grace has her own plan.

28:51.380 --> 28:52.220
From this day on,

28:52.380 --> 28:54.180
you shall all take orders from Yan Ke

28:54.380 --> 28:55.900
to hunt down the rebels.

28:56.180 --> 28:58.490
All captives shall be executed

28:58.660 --> 28:59.860
as a warning to others.

29:05.700 --> 29:07.380
Yes, Your Grace.

29:20.530 --> 29:21.370
Let's go.

29:42.860 --> 29:43.700
Your Ladyship.

29:50.620 --> 29:51.460
Your Ladyship,

29:52.250 --> 29:53.900
our world is in utter chaos.

29:55.140 --> 29:56.980
But Her Grace keeps herself indoors.

29:58.180 --> 29:59.330
What does she mean by that?

30:00.330 --> 30:01.700
I don't really know.

30:01.700 --> 30:03.530
This is indeed a bit weird.

30:07.460 --> 30:09.010
When Her Grace gave this order,

30:10.050 --> 30:11.010
was anything unusual?

30:16.770 --> 30:17.730
If you ask me that,

30:18.090 --> 30:19.980
I recall she sounded a bit weak

30:20.860 --> 30:22.290
when she talked to me.

30:24.290 --> 30:27.010
These days, she's been hunting puppets.

30:28.290 --> 30:29.330
Could it be...?

30:29.490 --> 30:30.810
Are you saying

30:31.460 --> 30:32.900
Her Grace might be injured?

30:35.250 --> 30:36.290
Did she have a fight

30:36.290 --> 30:37.220
with Bai Sanxing?

32:18.050 --> 32:18.940
Bai Sanxing,

32:20.810 --> 32:22.290
so you really are being controlled.

33:48.530 --> 33:49.700
You're indeed

33:49.700 --> 33:50.730
my strongest puppet.

33:52.380 --> 33:53.220
Well done.

33:58.700 --> 33:59.540
He Simu.

34:00.180 --> 34:03.010
You didn't see this coming, did you?

34:16.820 --> 34:18.090
Don't try to release your power

34:18.090 --> 34:19.380
to destroy my body.

34:20.740 --> 34:22.460
I'm shielded by a magical artifact.

34:23.690 --> 34:24.530
Today,

34:25.060 --> 34:25.920
I will drain

34:25.930 --> 34:27.490
every bit of your power until you die.

35:45.880 --> 35:51.210
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

35:51.540 --> 35:55.790
♪Light encountered shadow♪

35:57.150 --> 36:02.520
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

36:02.820 --> 36:07.420
♪The unbreakable fate♪

36:08.510 --> 36:10.350
♪Suddenly cracked♪

36:22.560 --> 36:28.000
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

36:28.180 --> 36:32.510
♪Light encountered shadow♪

36:33.880 --> 36:39.270
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

36:39.500 --> 36:43.440
♪The unbreakable fate♪

36:45.210 --> 36:47.100
♪Suddenly cracked♪

36:49.760 --> 36:52.920
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

36:52.920 --> 36:55.450
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

36:55.450 --> 37:00.970
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

37:00.970 --> 37:04.210
♪Following fate's guidance♪

37:04.210 --> 37:09.070
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

37:09.410 --> 37:12.430
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

37:12.430 --> 37:15.250
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

37:15.510 --> 37:18.040
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

37:18.040 --> 37:23.460
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

37:23.630 --> 37:26.700
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

37:26.860 --> 37:31.760
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

37:31.970 --> 37:35.440
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
